<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 | System Failure</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body { 
            background-color: #0f172a; 
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; 
            height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .failure-container {
            max-width: 600px; width: 90%; text-align: center;
        }
        .icon-box {
            width: 80px; height: 80px; background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            color: #ef4444; border-radius: 20px; display: flex;
            align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
        }
        .error-log {
            background: #1e293b; border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #334155;
            margin: 2rem 0; font-family: 'monospace'; font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .btn-recover {
            background: #ef4444; color: white; border: none;
            padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 700;
            transition: 0.3s; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;
        }
        .btn-recover:hover { background: #dc2626; color: white; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="failure-container">
        <div class="icon-box">
            <i class="fas fa-bolt fa-2x"></i>
        </div>
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-800">System Interruption</h1>
        <p class="text-secondary">The server encountered an unexpected condition and was unable to fulfill your request.</p>
        
        <div class="error-log">
            <div class="text-danger mb-1 fw-bold">Runtime.Exception:</div>
            <div class="text-white-50 small">
                <%= typeof errorMessage !== 'undefined' ? errorMessage : "Trace ID: " + Math.random().toString(36).substr(2, 9).toUpperCase() %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center gap-3">
            <a href="/admin" class="btn-recover w-100">
                Attempt System Recovery
            </a>
            <p class="small text-muted">If this persists, please contact technical support.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>